added.description: Changes where you add to the project.

removed.description: Changes where you removed a feature or something else.

fixed.description: Changes where you fixed a bug.

security.description: Changes where you made an update for security reasons.

deprecated.description: Changes where you plan on removing something, but are waiting to do so.

version.description: The current version of the project. If left off this will fallback to being `Unreleased`.

release_date.description: The release date of the current version. If this is property is not defined this will fall back to `TBD`.

notice.description: A notice for the current release.

change.description: The type of change you are creating. Valid values are `major` | `minor` | `patch`

simple_change_entry.description: This is a simple change entry.

flag.description: The flag to add a prefix to the changes.

references.description: List of references to this current change.

type.description: The type of reference, can be `pull_request`,`pr`, or `issue`

number.description: The pull request or issue number
